    "dashboard_clear_all_btn": "Διαγραφή all μαθητής records and επαναφορά analytics to empty. This is permanent and irreversible. All δεδομένα is removed: μαθητής identifiers, activity records, κουίζ βαθμολογία, and aggregate statistics. Χρήση with extreme caution. Scenarios for clearing: end of semester επαναφορά, testing with demo δεδομένα, or starting fresh with νέος τάξη. Consider exporting before clearing to preserve records. Confirmation requires explicit acknowledgment. After clearing, dashboard εμφανίζει no δεδομένα until νέος μαθητής join. This does not affect: your δημιουργήθηκε πόροι, αποθηκευμένο μάθημα, or δάσκαλος library. συμβουλή: Clear only when absolutely necessary; archives are usually preferable.",
    "dashboard_close_btn": "Exit the dashboard πίνακας and return to main workspace. Dashboard δεδομένα persists—reopening εμφανίζει same πληροφορίες. Changes made in dashboard (grading, notes) are αποθηκευμένο automatically before closing. Χρήση κλείσιμο to: return to περιεχόμενο creation, reduce οπτικός πολυπλοκότητα, or focus on other tasks. Dashboard can be reopened anytime from header. If connected to live συνεδρία, closing dashboard does not end the συνεδρία—μαθητής remain connected. Keyboard shortcut: Escape (in most views). Dashboard automatically closes when switching to major activities. Your current προβολή position is remembered for επόμενο opening.",
