    "persona_save_chat": "Preserve this conversation for future reference. Saving captures: ολοκλήρωση transcript with timestamps, reflection prompts and responses, and XP earned. Saved conversations appear in History for: reviewing what was learned, continuing conversations later, evidence for portfolios, and δάσκαλος αξιολόγηση. Conversations auto-αποθήκευση at conclusion, but χειροκίνητο αποθήκευση preserves mid-conversation πρόοδος. Multiple saves δημιουργία έκδοση snapshots. Saved chats can be: exported as έγγραφο, shared with δάσκαλος, and referenced in written assignments. συμβουλή: Αποθήκευση before major direction changes in case you want to return to earlier topics. δάσκαλος can πρόσβαση αποθηκευμένο conversations through dashboard.",
