    "escape_room_timer": "Countdown timer for the Escape Room experience. Time pressure δημιουργεί urgency and excitement while building time management δεξιότητα. ορατό to all team members simultaneously. When timer reaches zero: παιχνίδι ends, current πρόοδος is αποθηκευμένο, and partial completion βαθμολογία are calculated. Typical escape rooms εκτέλεση 15-30 minutes. δάσκαλος can: pause timer for οδηγία, προσθήκη time for struggling teams, or adjust initial time in ρυθμίσεις. Timer χρώμα changes (green to yellow to red) as time runs low. ήχος προειδοποίηση sounds at critical thresholds (unless muted). Time remaining affects final βαθμολογία—faster escapes earn bonus XP.",
