    "escape_room_lives": "Limited attempts σύστημα that adds consequence to guessing. Teams έναρξη with 3-5 lives (configurable). Each wrong απάντηση deducts one life. At zero lives: παιχνίδι over for the team, final βαθμολογία recorded, and επιλογές to restart or συνέχεια with reduced βαθμολογία. Lives σύστημα teaches: reading carefully before answering, collaborating to verify απάντηση, and managing risk. Lives can be restored by: δάσκαλος intervention, purchasing with XP (if enabled), or solving bonus puzzles. Remaining lives affect final βαθμολογία. οπτικός hearts display current life μετρήστε. Creates meaningful stakes without permanent consequence.",
