    "escape_room_leaderboard": "Real-time competitive standings showing all teams. Displays: team χρώμα, puzzles solved, time remaining, and ranking. Updates instantly as teams πρόοδος. Creates excitement and healthy competition. Leaderboard visibility is configurable: always ορατό (maximum competition), ορατό after checkpoints, or hidden until completion (focus λειτουργία). Teams in the lead δείτε their position, motivating continued effort; trailing teams δείτε the gap, encouraging acceleration. Final leaderboard εμφανίζει: completion time, accuracy, and bonus achievements. Leaderboard δεδομένα helps δάσκαλος identify teams needing υποστήριξη.",
