    "escape_room_hint_button": "Request assistance when stuck on a puzzle. Teams have limited υπόδειξη tokens (typically 2-3). Using a υπόδειξη: consumes one token, reveals a helpful clue (not the απάντηση), and may reduce XP earned for that puzzle. υπόδειξη are progressive—πρώτο υπόδειξη is subtle, subsequent υπόδειξη are περισσότερο direct. This teaches: trying multiple approaches before seeking βοήθεια, χρησιμοποιώντας πόροι strategically, and that asking for βοήθεια is okay. δάσκαλος can grant bonus υπόδειξη to struggling teams. υπόδειξη usage is tracked in analytics. Some puzzle types have ήχος or οπτικός υπόδειξη for accessibility. Χρήση υπόδειξη wisely—they do not regenerate.",
