    "escape_room_cipher_input": "κείμενο είσοδος for cipher or decoder puzzles. Cipher types συμπερίληψη: letter substitution, reverse κείμενο, αριθμός-to-letter codes, and πρώτο-letter acrostics. Διαβάστε the puzzle οδηγία carefully to κατανοήστε the encoding method. Type your decoded απάντηση exactly as requested (case-sensitivity varies by puzzle). Common σφάλμα: extra spaces, incorrect spelling, wrong case. υπόδειξη can βοήθεια with cipher method if stuck. Cipher puzzles teach: pattern recognition, systematic thinking, and attention to λεπτομέρεια. Some ciphers connect to λεξιλόγιο or θέμα from πηγή περιεχόμενο. Work collaboratively—different team members may spot patterns others miss. Check απάντηση before submitting to avoid life loss.",
