    "escape_room_sequence_container": "Sequencing puzzle where you arrange στοιχείο chronologically, alphabetically, or logically. Σύρετε στοιχείο to reorder, or χρήση arrow κουμπί for keyboard navigation. περιεχόμενο may be: historical events (chronological), ιστορία elements (plot order), process βήμα (procedural), or size/quantity (numerical). Correct order unlocks the puzzle. Check your sequence before submitting—review for any obvious σφάλμα. Sequencing teaches: temporal reasoning, cause-effect relationships, and organizational thinking. Some puzzles have partially correct feedback (showing which στοιχείο are in right position). Work systematically from what you know most confidently. Team discussion helps verify ordering logic.",
