    "persona_panel": "The AI Persona συνομιλία πίνακας - engage in authentic conversations with historical figures, scientists, literary χαρακτήρας, or προσαρμοσμένο personas. Uses προχωρημένο AI to simulate period-accurate speech patterns, knowledge, and perspectives. Perfect for primary πηγή analysis, perspective-taking, and empathy-building exercises. υποστήριξη multiple response λειτουργία: In-χαρακτήρας (fully immersive), Educational (with learning scaffolds), or Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "An AI persona ready for conversation. Each κάρτα εμφανίζει the χαρακτήρας's name, time period, and expertise εμβαδόν. Κάντε κλικ to έναρξη an interview - the AI will respond authentically based on their historical context, beliefs, and knowledge. Χρήση personas for primary πηγή analysis, perspective-taking exercises, or creative writing inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Δημιουργία AI personas automatically from your πηγή περιεχόμενο. The σύστημα analyzes your κείμενο to identify key figures, historical periods, or χαρακτήρας archetypes and δημιουργεί authentic conversational partners. Generated personas συμπερίληψη accurate biographical λεπτομέρεια, period-appropriate λεξιλόγιο, and contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know about events after their time).",
    "persona_select_button": "Επιλέξτε this persona to begin your interview or conversation. Once επιλεγμένο, you'll εισάγετε an immersive συνομιλία interface where you can ask ερώτηση, εξερεύνηση their perspective, and earn XP for meaningful exchanges. The AI responds based on the χαρακτήρας's historical knowledge, personality, and cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return to the persona selection screen to επιλέξτε a different χαρακτήρας. Your current conversation πρόοδος is automatically αποθηκευμένο, and you can return to συνέχεια it later. This allows exploring multiple perspectives on the same historical topic.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Προσθήκη συγκεκριμένος requirements for how the persona should behave during conversations. παράδειγμα: focus on a συγκεκριμένος time period, emphasize certain beliefs or τιμή, maintain particular speech patterns, or limit responses to historically accurate knowledge. δάσκαλος can χρήση this to align personas with συγκεκριμένος learning objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Επιλέξτε how the persona responds to δημιουργία different learning experiences. IN χαρακτήρας: Fully immersive historical φωνή with no modern explanations. EDUCATIONAL: χαρακτήρας speaks but περιλαμβάνει learning scaffolds, λεξιλόγιο υποστήριξη, and context. MIXED: Balanced approach with authentic φωνή plus occasional clarifications. Επιλέξτε based on μαθητής readiness and learning στόχος.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type your own άνοιγμα-ended response instead of selecting from pre-written επιλογές. Free response λειτουργία promotes creative expression, critical thinking, and authentic dialogue δεξιότητα. Responses are analyzed for historical accuracy, empathy, and βάθος of inquiry. Higher-quality ερώτηση earn περισσότερο XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Εμφάνιση or απόκρυψη response suggestions and conversation υπόδειξη. When enabled, the σύστημα provides scaffolded ερώτηση starters, historical context prompts, and engagement suggestions. Helpful for μαθητής νέος to historical inquiry or those needing υποστήριξη with άνοιγμα-ended questioning. δάσκαλος can απενεργοποίηση υπόδειξη for περισσότερο προχωρημένο αξιολόγηση scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Display helpful υπόδειξη for engaging with the persona. υπόδειξη συμπερίληψη historically relevant ερώτηση to ask, topics the χαρακτήρας would find interesting, and prompts that lead to deeper understanding. Great for μαθητής who need scaffolding or aren't sure how to begin a historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Αποστολή your μήνυμα to the persona χαρακτήρας. Your ερώτηση or response is analyzed for relevance and βάθος. The AI persona will respond authentically based on their historical context, knowledge, and personality. Well-crafted ερώτηση that εμφάνιση historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Κλείσιμο the persona conversation πίνακας. Your συνομιλία history and earned XP are automatically αποθηκευμένο. You can resume this conversation later from the History tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Κλείσιμο Persona συνομιλία",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Γράψτε your reflection on the conversation for αξιολόγηση. Reflect on what you learned about the historical figure, how their perspective differs from modern viewpoints, and how this conversation changed your understanding. Reflections are evaluated χρησιμοποιώντας a rubric aligned to historical thinking δεξιότητα and can earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End the conversation and δημιουργία a comprehensive summary of your discussion. The summary περιλαμβάνει: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality of your ερώτηση, empathy demonstrated, and XP earned. This summary can be exported for αξιολόγηση, added to μαθητής portfolios, or χρησιμοποιήθηκε as a writing prompt for reflection activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Αποθήκευση this conversation to review or κοινοποίηση later. Saved chats preserve the ολοκλήρωση dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, and any reflections. Χρήση αποθηκευμένο chats for μαθητής portfolios, αξιολόγηση evidence, τάξη discussions, or exemplar models. Saved conversations can be exported as PDF or shared with other μαθητής.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get a conversation starter or topic suggestion when you're not sure what to ask. The σύστημα δημιουργεί historically relevant ερώτηση based on the persona's background, expertise, and time period. Great for overcoming writer's block or discovering νέος γωνία to εξερεύνηση in your historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically αποστολή your μήνυμα when you διακοπή typing for a few seconds. Creates a περισσότερο natural conversational flow, especially when χρησιμοποιώντας φωνή dictation. Απενεργοποίηση this if you prefer to review and επεξεργασία μήνυμα before sending, or if you need περισσότερο time to compose thoughtful responses.",
