    "timeline_topic": "The main topic or θέμα of the timeline being δημιουργήθηκε. The AI δημιουργεί historically accurate events based on this topic and your πηγή περιεχόμενο. παράδειγμα topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle of Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events are automatically ordered chronologically for sequencing εξάσκηση.",
    "timeline_count": "αριθμός of events to συμπερίληψη in the timeline. περισσότερο events δημιουργία longer, περισσότερο λεπτομερές timelines but increase δυσκολία. Recommended: 4-6 events for beginners, 8-10 for μεσαίο, 12+ for προχωρημένο learners. Events are draggable for sequencing εξάσκηση after generation.",
